Description:
    Generates a contact page that creates an activity in the WebCRM. To create an example use the
    "--cms_path" parameter.

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:contact_page`
    `rails generate cms:component:contact_page --cms_path=/website/en`

    CMS: obj_class ContactPage
    CMS: attribute title (html)
    CMS: attribute body (html)
    CMS: attribute show_in_navigation (enum)
    CMS: attribute sort_key (string)
    CMS: attribute crm_activity_type (string)
    CRM: Activity type 'contact-form' with attributes 'email' and 'message'